---
title: One-Pot Mexican Beef Rump & Bean Veggie Soup with Cheddar Cheese & Corn Chips
description: This flavour combo is a beloved companion to many dishes like enchiladas, nachos and tacos. Let's add another one to the list with a Mexican flavoured soup! It won’t disappoint, in fact it may be the new way to eat beans, veggies and cheese.

